Simple VPC with private and public subnets, internet gateway to allow connection
to internet, and NAT Gateway to enable private subnet to connect to internet
(may be needed for the private instance to update packages), while still
disallowing public inbound traffic.

This is a manual VPC setup (not using terraform's VPC module).

Careful when applying this as NAT Gatway is not free tier eligible and will
incur costs even when unattached.
